Some issue with publishing toolstate I don't understand, it looks like it failed to upload something?

@Joshua Nelson I think that is normal. The actual work is still being done on azure (https://dev.azure.com/rust-lang/rust/_build). The github actions are just going through the motions, but aren't configured to publish anything (otherwise the two CI systems would be tripping over each other).
Oh I see, this is the continuous deploy bit, not continuous integration. That makes sense, thanks!
